- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a relevant sub-category because the paper deals with the analysis of engineering and physical systems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is possible because the paper involves programming in a specific language (HOL-Light) to conduct the formal analysis. 
- cs.ET (Emerging Technologies) is a possibility because the paper proposes a novel approach to frequency domain analysis of continuous time systems using higher-order-logic theorem proving, which can be seen as an emerging technology in the field.
